Day 84: Copy Data to App Servers using Ansible

Date: December 16, 2025
Overview
Used Ansible to distribute files across multiple servers.
Key Concepts Learned

Copy module
Template module
File permissions
Idempotency

Commands Used
yaml- name: Copy configuration file
  copy:
    src: /local/config.conf
    dest: /etc/app/config.conf
    owner: root
    group: root
    mode: '0644'

Challenges Faced
File ownership and permission issues on target servers.
